  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/OpenDirectory\/odattributetype\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T20:24:22Z\n---\n\n# _ODAttributeType\n\n**Article**\n\nAn Open Directory attribute type.\n\n## Overview\n\nThis is an intermediary type. Use [doc:\/\/com.apple.opendirectory\/documentation\/OpenDirectory\/ODAttributeType] instead.\n\n## Data Types\n\n- **ODAttributeType**: An Open Directory attribute type.\n- **ODAuthenticationType**: An Open Directory authentication type.\n- **ODContext**: An Open Directory context type.\n- **ODNodeRef**: An Open Directory node type.\n- **ODQueryRef**: An Open Directory query type.\n- **ODRecordRef**: An Open Directory record type.\n- **ODSessionRef**: An Open Directory session type.\n- **ODMatchType**: An Open Directory match type.\n- **ODNodeType**: An Open Directory node type.\n- **ODQueryCallback**: A callback function called as results from a scheduled query are returned.\n- **ODRecordType**: An Open Directory record type.\n- **_ODAuthenticationType**: An Open Directory authentication type.\n- **_ODRecordType**: An Open Directory record type.\n\n",
